snippet.title: Kozue’s Strange Journey 2 - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
One year after taking down the supernatural threat behind a series of disappearances, Sayuri Shirasagi joins back up with her friends to fight the Shadows and unravel the mystery distorting the world once more!
